{"id":22215,"title":"Hand hygiene in the dental setting: reducing the risk of infection.","abstract":"Hand hygiene remains the single most important measure for reducing the risk of healthcare-associated infections. In the past 20 years, hand-washing recommendations and guidelines have become increasingly complex, and a plethora of products have become available. This article aims to discuss and clarify the fundamentals of appropriate hand hygiene in dentistry. ","date":"2014-02-25","categories":"Bacterial Infections and Mycoses","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24564616","annotations":[{"name":"Dentistry","weight":0.115427,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dentistry"},{"name":"Infection","weight":0.0619293,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Infection"},{"name":"Hand washing","weight":0.0321906,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hand_washing"},{"name":"Risk","weight":0.0248395,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Risk"},{"name":"Complex number","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Complex_number"},{"name":"Single (music)","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Single_(music)"},{"name":"Product (chemistry)","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Product_(chemistry)"},{"name":"Risk of infection","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Risk_of_infection"},{"name":"Hand","weight":0.0157947,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hand"},{"name":"Measure (mathematics)","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Measure_(mathematics)"},{"name":"Hygiene","weight":0.0142619,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hygiene"}]}
